<p></p>
<p>Well, here&rsquo;s an interesting meme from <a href="http://www.vecosys.com/2007/03/11/imagini-where-myers-briggs-meets-image-labeller-in-order-to-meet-someone-like-you/">Sam Sethi</a> via Robert Scoble&rsquo;s Google Reader shared items.&nbsp; I&rsquo;m not into Myers-Briggs (that should be a category here, huh?) but I met my wife Vicki by acting out a horoscope.</p>
<p>I wouldn&rsquo;t play this game except that I found the graphical and visual experience very nice.&nbsp; Here&rsquo;s a nifty way to put a little glamour on my blog page.</p>
<p>Happy Daylight Savings Time Morning, you wild and crazy North Americans.</p>
